 Beware minor Spoiler

i dunno his name... but i liked the guy... he was umm.. "goofy"... and well... he had a crush on Carter, and he knew something about O'neill and Carter which he ever so often tried to confirm, with his questions to the Major...

i loved the scene where the bomb explodes in the house and Barret and Carter jump out.... he falls on top of her and Carter asks: What are you doing?

Barret answers : Covering You.
Carter (breathing heavily) annoyingly answers : Thank you... now get UP!

Barret gets really shaken up and quietly says... "yeah...right" and gets up...
truly funny and CLASSIC
